%% Diagram: IME composition sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User (CJK keyboard)
    participant IME as OS IME
    participant DOM as contentEditable
    participant Editor as Editor state

    User->>IME: keystroke
    IME->>DOM: compositionstart
    DOM->>Editor: mark isComposing = true
    loop one or more updates
        IME->>DOM: compositionupdate (provisional text)
        DOM->>Editor: show preview only
        IME->>DOM: beforeinput insertCompositionText
        Note right of DOM: NOT cancelable
        DOM->>DOM: native DOM update
    end
    User->>IME: confirm candidate
    IME->>DOM: compositionend (final text)
    DOM->>Editor: commit text + clear isComposing
    DOM->>Editor: input event fires
